<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<Weakness xmlns="http://cwe.mitre.org/cwe-7" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" ID="758" Name="Reliance on Undefined, Unspecified, or Implementation-Defined Behavior" Abstraction="Class" Structure="Simple" Status="Incomplete">
         <Description>The product uses an API function, data structure, or other entity in a way that relies on properties that are not always guaranteed to hold for that entity.</Description>
         <Extended_Description>This can lead to resultant weaknesses when the required properties change, such as when the product is ported to a different platform or if an interaction error (CWE-435) occurs.</Extended_Description>
         <Related_Weaknesses>
            <Related_Weakness Nature="ChildOf" CWE_ID="710" View_ID="1000" Ordinal="Primary" />
         </Related_Weaknesses>
